net.markenwerk.commons.iterables

Interface ProtectedIterable<Payload>

  • Type Parameters:
    Payload - The payload type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<Payload>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EnumerationIterable, InfiniteIterable, LookAheadIterable, ProtectingIterable, StringTokenizerIterable

    public interface ProtectedIterable<Payload>
extends Iterable<Payload>
    A ProtectedIterable is an Iterable that guarantees that every call to Iterable.iterator() yields a ProtectedIterator.
    Since:
    2.2.0
    Author:
    Torsten Krause (tk at markenwerk dot net)
